text: tanna kattadavannu allahana bhaya hagu avana meccugeya bunadiya mele kattidavanu sresthano, athava avanannu hottu narakakke kusidu bilaliruva, bhari hondavondara asthira ancinalliruva bunadiya mele tanna kattadavannu kattidavanu sresthano? Akramigala pangadakke allahanu saridari torisuvudilla
